    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 1d — Scanner (JobSpy)\n\n**Self-hosted only.** Requires `jobspy-scanner` Docker sidecar on port 3457.\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Read enabled JobSpy queries from Search Queries table\n2. Send all queries to sidecar `/batch` endpoint in one call\n3. Parse results, apply geography filter, generate Job IDs\n4. Deduplicate against existing Pipeline records\n5. Create net-new records in Pipeline\n\n**Schedule:** Daily 8:15am (after 1a/1b/1c)\n\n**Safety brakes:**\n- Max 100 results per query (sidecar)\n- Max 10 queries per batch (sidecar)\n- Max 100 net-new records per run (dedup node)\n\n**To add queries:** Edit the Search Queries table in Airtable. Set Source Type = JobSpy, Enabled = checked.",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 380
